text: Roberta Stewart (born 16 June 1981) is a New Zealand water polo player. She competed for the New Zealand women's national water polo team in the 2007 World Aquatics Championships. She played for Marist club in Auckland, and Long Beach State University. == References == == Other websites == * roberta- stewart-of-new-zealand, Getty Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
